'''Ledriq''' (s tgutit : {{Lang|got|𐌷𐍂𐍉𐌸𐌰𐍂𐌴𐌹𐌺𐍃/Hroþareiks}}, s tesbenyulit : Rodrigo, s [[Tutlayt taɛrabt]] : {{Lang|arabe|لذريق}}), yemmut di yulyu 711 deg [[Spenyul]] d agellid aneggaru n yigutiyen n umalu imi tamurt-is kecmen-tt yinselmen s ddaw n tmela n ''Tareq u ziyad d'' ''Musa bnu Nusayr'' .

== Tudert ==
d mmi-s n twacult n lesyad .

Tamnaḍt taǧaret n [[Tafriqt Ugafa|Tmazɣa]] kecmen-tt yisnemen s ddaw n tmehla n [[Musa bnu Nusayr]] . Aneggaru-agi yerra yiwen n umaziɣ kra nniḍen nnan-d d amwali ( yiwen n yimsuqel amaynut ) aẓar-is d amaziɣ , d [[Ṭareq u Ziyad]] d anembaḍ ɣef Ṭenǧa , yernu imehl-as akken 7 000 n yimnayen yettwasuqqlen ɣer [[Tineslemt|tneslemt]] mebla tarlkint . 

Lkunt Yulyan , anembaḍ n Sebta , qi wumi ssawalen wid n Turuft Julyan ,yella yekreh Ledriq yernu yettemsefham d Ṭareq . Yules-d umazran amaṣri Ibn Ɛebd El Ḥakam snat n tasutin umbeɛd belli yelli-s n Yulyan : Flurinda terza ɣer tgelda n Ledriq akken ad d-lmed maca yekkes fella-s lḥerma-s tuɣal-d ɣer Sebta s tadist .
